'statue' 'Astier' 'laughing' 'glowing statue' 'laughing statue' 'Astier's Statue'~
Sit on a pillar which rises out form the lake, is a glowing green statue
which has great resemblence to the god astier, dressed in his normal pictated
grab, a tight pair of paint, with a checkard quiltited style to them,
along with a matching shirt. A hat with 4 branches with bells on them,
that is assosiated with most jesters. At his waist is an actual sheathed
rapier, which his left hand rest on, making it imposible to take of of
the statue, the blade is emiting an odd laughing sound, which can be heard
from far away. Astiers face is smiling, tho a tear hangs from his right
eye.
~
